==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] [[θεραπευτικός]] (''therapeftikos'') "attentive, helpful, obliging, curative", from [[θεραπεία]] "[[therapy]]".
===Adjective===
'''Therapeutic'''
#Of, or relating to [[therapy]]
#Having [[healing]] [[power]]s; [[curative]], [[remedial]]

